  "detailed_description": "<h1>⚔️🐸♟️MY OTHER GAMES! ⚔️🐸♟️</h1><p><table>\t<tr>\t\t<td></td>\t\t<td></td></tr></table></p><br><h1>-</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Embark in a procedurally generated journey in FROGUE, a Roguelike Bullet Hell Platformer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/e1997551f4158b8bd5fb2e1461ff5363.poster.avif?t=1707919231\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/e1997551f4158b8bd5fb2e1461ff5363.webm?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/e1997551f4158b8bd5fb2e1461ff5363.mp4?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dash to avoid bullet and kill your enemies!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/f85d1b06815804e844aa1c469bd99347.poster.avif?t=1707919231\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/f85d1b06815804e844aa1c469bd99347.webm?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/f85d1b06815804e844aa1c469bd99347.mp4?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>​​​<br>Throw knifes to kill them at a distance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/315dac0489be6b07eaa5a7e66e17fc30.poster.avif?t=1707919231\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/315dac0489be6b07eaa5a7e66e17fc30.webm?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/315dac0489be6b07eaa5a7e66e17fc30.mp4?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Out of options? No problem, freeze time and make your own solution!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/3e4694ebc41c667889df329a87a7cf91.poster.avif?t=1707919231\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/3e4694ebc41c667889df329a87a7cf91.webm?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936990/extras/3e4694ebc41c667889df329a87a7cf91.mp4?t=1707919231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>​​",
